Converts a [`String`] into an [`Owned`] variant.
No heap allocation is performed, and the string
is not copied.

# Example

```
# use std::borrow::Cow;
let s = "eggplant".to_string();
let s2 = "eggplant".to_string();
assert_eq!(Cow::from(s), Cow::<'static, str>::Owned(s2));
```

